Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}怖がらず開けてね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.54,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Flying far away
